Wow I haven't written in a long time but it's not like I have had anything good to say anyway so I took a survey.

Emotions

Created by andy and taken 7179 times on bzoink!

+ Basics +
Are you emotional :Very.
Do songs make you cry? If so, name a few :"Burger Queen" by Placebo, "With or Without you" by U2 and that one song Dusty makes me listen to by Thursday
What about movies :Tuck Everlasting and Moulin Rouge
What emotion do you usually feel :Anxious, Sad
+ Sadness +
What does it take to make you cry your heart out :Uhm....The feeling of me being alone and lost in this big scary world and hating everything and wanting to end it all.
How many times have you done that :about 5 times
Where do you cry :In the Shower
Do you hate crying :No I like it but it doesn't help make the pain go away.
Do you like it when others cry :Unless it's for a stupid reason and I can laugh at them
Do you think tears make eyes look pretty :Well if they're ugly, they aint never going to be pretty. Some people look good when they cry others just look like shit.
Who looks good when they cry :Any boy who crys because that shows they're sensative.
How else do you express sadness :I scream like really loud and I usually end up doing something I maybe shouldn't have done.
Are you sad all the time :Most of it.
+ Anger +
What does it take to make you mad :Uh usually I don't get sad, I get jealous.
What do you do when you're angry :I scream, I cry and then I go kick the shit out of whoever made me that way.
How short is your temper :I'm impatient but it doesn't take alot to get me annoyed and then go off on your dumb ass.
How long does it take you to calm down :I'm mellow dramatic so not very long, i end up forgetting about it.
What's the worst thing you've done when you were mad :I cut my arm to piss my mom off.
Do you freak out when others are angry :Depends on if they are crazy.
Has anyone ever recommended anger management to you :No thank god.
What's the worst thing someone's done to make you mad :Uh I don't remember.
Do you anger people :Probably because I'm so annoying.
+ Joy +
How often are you happy :Not very often. Never purely happy.
What makes you happy :Kisses, Hugs, laughing, drinking, parties,
What do you do when you're happy :I laugh, I run around and talk to people I don't know.
How optimistic are you :I'm more pessimistic but I'll try new things and do crazy shit I don't know what you would call that.
Do happy people make you mad :Sometimes because I'm not them.
What's the worst thing someone can do while they're happy :KIll someone.
Ever been so happy you were dying to tell everyone :I've ran around like a crazy person and prolly gave off that vibe.
Ever been so happy you cried :In movies.
Do you smile a lot :I do.
Kiss people a lot:I wish.
Who really makes you happy :Brad, Keith, Dusty, Jesse when he's not being stupid.
Do you like doing things for people when you're happy :I usualyl am more up to helping when happy.
+ Fear +
What do you do when you're scared :I cry in a corner.
What scares you :the easter bunny or anything in a suit and my own mind.
Do you like scaring people :No because it's scary
Do you like the trill of being frightened :I like the rush but I'd rather get that rush during sex or something other than shitting my pants.
Does fear accompany anger in your case :Sometimes.
Ever been so scared you couldn't breathe :I don't remember.
How often do you panic :I don't know. not as much as I used to. I remember I would run into people and FREAK out.
What's the one thing that scared you more than anything else EVER :Feeling like everyone questions me.
What do you do to calm your nerves :I try to get my mind off of it but it doesn't work.
Do rollercoasters scare you :Sometimes.
+ The strongest emotion +
What song never fails to get your strongest emotions going :hmmm....."Would I lie to you?" by Charles & Eddie and "Screaming Infidelities" by Dashboard Confessional
Movie :The Secret Garden and Girl, interrupted
Commericial :That really stupid car one.
Person :Dusty and any hot guy really. Brandon, and IDK who else.
Thing :Cigarettes and Kisses!
Sight :A big drop.....UGGG
Sound :When you cuddle, that breathing sound.
Food :Mashed Potatoes.!
Thing you're looking forward to/want :Moving in with Burt and getting a house!
+ What do you do +
When the emotion suck :I pout then I get over it
When the emotion rocks :I go all out.
When there's no emotion :I sit in complete silence.
+ Would you rather +
Never feel again :No man feeling numb is no good thing.
Feel loneliness or anger for the rest of your life :Neither. I want to be happy.
Be happy forever and never experience bad times :No i'd want something bad to happen eventually.
Cause misery :Can there be no misery?
Feel misery :Uhm....None?
Be alone :No....Hell No. I feel that when I'm not.
Be with everyone you know :I'd need some new peope in there.
+ Who +
Cheers you up more than anyone else :Nicole, Brad, Duckie
Angers you more than anyone else :Jesse.
Scares you more than anyone else :Mandy.
Makes you think about your emotions more than anyone else :Dusty!
Makes you really care about how they feel and what they think :Dusty! no man you can't be in two all alone.....uhm....Sarah?
